######################################################################################################################
# PURPOSE: This script is used to demonstrate the weblogic functionality. Basically it implements load balancer      #
#          with apache server and database used is MySQL.                                                            # 
# This script creates a data souce on the weblogic admin server for the sample application dukesbank                 #
